{"tid":1508952,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔會嬲五毛話玩fake news 我只會恨果班同意嘅人","createTime":"2019-08-26T16:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T21:20:28.000Z","uid":76845,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"08ba1a86becd2156fb29e6b739a3077c762e6933","tid":1508952,"uid":76845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"忍唔住出post<br />\n如果你唔係五毛但同意玩fake news只可以講你真係on9同蠢同對你班連登仔好失望<br />\n咁耐以黎示威者一直係用弱勢姿態挑戰強權<br />\n共產黨一路嘅手法就係玩抹黑黎打擊弱勢<br />\n依加你用共產黨手法去將我地由弱勢轉做強勢<br />\n去令港共政權變成弱勢 將我地咁耐建立嘅嘢毁於一旦<br />\n大家起得連登大部分都讀過下書 <br />\n大家識講唔係黃藍問題 係黑白問題 唔該唔好得把口<br />\n自己用腦去判斷每一個行動長遠對場運動係咪有利<br />\n唔好人做你做 特別起依個時候充斥咁多五毛<br />\n懇請不要被仇恨支配自己 時刻提醒自己同身邊人"},{"pid":"421eb455dadd49fab2235a7d8dc75ee5ad57a75f","tid":1508952,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=94103ea0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=fd106b0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=0a1086c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"3f55776c9f86a4eecfc4ed0d088e9b66329c5e1d","tid":1508952,"uid":76845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:38:33.00